desc: Community Supported Agriculture in Kern County, California. Grass Fed Beef and Lamb, Pork & Poultry Raised on Pasture. Items can be shipped, picked up at a local farmers market or delivered by our farm staff in areas within Los Angeles and Kern Counties.
